   <body>
      <p>This feature enables you to add one or more participants in the program.</p>
      <p>To add a participant, please follow the below steps:</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Go to the Participants page.</li>
         <li>Click Add Participant.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432701/107118614.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Enter or select the participants' name which you want to add, in the Account Name column. Please view the below image.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432701/107118613.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Click Save.<p>The participant is added.</p>
            <note type="note">
               <p>Note</p>
               <p>The system will throw a validation if the same participant is added multiple times in an overlapping time period.</p>
            </note>
         </li>
      </ol>
